{"tid":2454267,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"棄上訴入獄 逆權司機籲手足堅持","createTime":"2021-03-20T06:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T08:51:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5ad1454d531ce6ddfa30e8e31c76358200b7c57a","tid":2454267,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:02:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210320/GKE6K3KL2JD2PP36LV6C5SERQI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210320%2FGKE6K3KL2JD2PP36LV6C5SERQI%2F&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDJszS%2Fgy1fqSqMk7TcT3QhU%3D&h=97c412e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210320%2FGKE6K3KL2JD2PP36LV6C5SERQI%2F&h=81481cc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210320/GKE6K3KL2JD2PP36LV6C5SERQI/</a><br />\n<br />\n棄上訴入獄 逆權司機籲手足堅持<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方前年7月7日驅散九龍區大遊行示威者期間，一名曾任警務人員的六旬司機，將的士橫泊在彌敦道行車路，阻止警方推進防線，其間拒絕按警員指示駛走車輛，並涉踢警員。的士司機早前因襲警及阻差辦公判監六個月，他原定昨天就定罪及刑罰上訴，但開庭後親自向法官陳慶偉表示放棄上訴，即時入獄服刑。他在開庭前親筆寄語手足「記住堅持」及「加油」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9Wzyyv0PetKmln56XAMbFkCB_HQ=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5WFSOZI2UJBCHHSYSORP4EDITI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9Wzyyv0PetKmln56XAMbFkCB_HQ%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5WFSOZI2UJBCHHSYSORP4EDITI.jpg&h=171e353d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■前年九龍區大遊行，張錦運（白衣者）將的士橫泊在警方防線前。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾任警察 襲警阻差兩罪成<br />\n<br />\n曾任警察的上訴人張錦運（68歲）昨穿涼鞋步入高等法院。他向本報記者手寫了幾句打氣說話，「謝各位手足，記住堅持！加油」，署名為「張錦運，逆權司機」。<br />\n<br />\n被問到有甚麼說話向香港人講，張無奈謂「仲有乜好講吖，係咪？你睇吓黎生！」他稱自己頂得住，反叮囑記者保重身體。<br />\n<br />\n上訴人早前被裁定阻撓正。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官鄭潤聰裁決時指，警。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCMA344/20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1QlQUDSYjIjn7lkMMczJp_Jkoeg=/802x909/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IGLE3CUWKRD53LSMWORVBR6D5Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1QlQUDSYjIjn7lkMMczJp_Jkoeg%3D%2F802x909%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIGLE3CUWKRD53LSMWORVBR6D5Q.jpg&h=57b1c0aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張錦運<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fAMldMaqdUZLxB6yjL6j5L31atw=/802x854/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EVFTFFPODVFUFH6YN6OEABS54U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfAMldMaqdUZLxB6yjL6j5L31atw%3D%2F802x854%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEVFTFFPODVFUFH6YN6OEABS54U.jpg&h=179d1418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■上訴人張錦運服刑前寫上打氣字條。"},{"pid":"3748ebf9b2b019f3deb99fa1be6c516c3969a13d","tid":2454267,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:33:12.000Z","msg":"保重"},{"pid":"d0bf68a7195dc7f7b3de875fe4d26a4818483420","tid":2454267,"uid":70501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:56:23.000Z","msg":"手字好靚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19d33f15a5e341f8442757f96ce5ab315d604f6","tid":2454267,"uid":112878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:57:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fad342db7afb7ed717b3db4439b71a48b955e9bf","tid":2454267,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"Respect<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196a9dbe1651123fa16b49a501a6459830a21117","tid":2454267,"uid":220292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:51:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hk